<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Strpos on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/strpos/</link><description>Recent content in Strpos on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/strpos/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>PHP Warning: strpos(): Empty needle</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-strpos/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-strpos/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="php-warning-strpos-empty-needle"&gt;PHP Warning: strpos(): Empty needle&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This warning occurs when you pass an empty string as the needle (search term) to &lt;code&gt;strpos()&lt;/code&gt;. The function requires a non-empty string to search for within the haystack.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passing an uninitialized or empty variable as the needle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Not trimming or validating input before searching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using string interpolation that results in an empty value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="validate-the-needle-before-searching"&gt;Validate the Needle Before Searching&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong — needle may be empty
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$needle &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$pos &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;strpos&lt;/span&gt;($haystack, $needle);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct — check first
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;empty&lt;/span&gt;($needle)) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; $pos &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;strpos&lt;/span&gt;($haystack, $needle);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; $pos &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-the-null-coalescing-operator"&gt;Use the Null Coalescing Operator&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$pos &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;strpos&lt;/span&gt;($haystack, $needle &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;??&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-strlen-before-strpos"&gt;Check strlen() Before strpos()&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeStrpos&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; $haystack, &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; $needle)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ($needle &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;strlen&lt;/span&gt;($needle) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;strpos&lt;/span&gt;($haystack, $needle);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-php" data-lang="php"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;php&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// This triggers the warning
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;$needle &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;strpos&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, $needle);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Warning: strpos(): Empty needle
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;strpos&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// 6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;?&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-strlen/"&gt;PHP Warning: strlen()&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/warning-in-array-search/"&gt;PHP Warning: array_search()&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/php/notice-undefined-index/"&gt;PHP Notice: Undefined Index&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>